name: Jack Reacher Collection
overview: An action crime thriller film series based on novels by author Lee Child based on Jack Reacher. Reacher roams the United States taking odd jobs and investigating suspicious and frequently dangerous situations.

parts.overview: When a gunman takes five lives with six shots, all evidence points to the suspect in custody. On interrogation, the suspect offers up a single note: "Get Jack Reacher!" So begins an extraordinary chase for the truth, pitting Jack Reacher against an unexpected enemy, with a skill for violence and a secret to keep.
parts.title: Jack Reacher

parts.overview: When Major Susan Turner is arrested for treason, ex-investigator Jack Reacher undertakes the challenging task to prove her innocence and ends up exposing a shocking conspiracy.
parts.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
